description: Some are well known, some forgotten, but all played a key role in World War Two.
title: Spy princess and Lady Death: Eight women of WW2
title_page: Spy princess and Lady Death: Eight women of WW2 - BBC News
maintext: She would dress up and go on dates with German soldiers to get information. "A little powder and a little drink on the way, and I'd pass their posts and wink and say, 'Do you want to search me?' God, what a flirtatious little bastard I was," she told the Australian newspaper.
